      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a pretty broad overview, but I'm trying to get a better sense of the actual character of these groups. Like, when you say they interact through \"competition\" or \"mistrust,\" are we talking about specific tribal characteristics that make some groups more prone to conflict or aggression than others? Just trying to understand if there are certain cultural or ethnic traits I should be aware of for our field staff.",
