    "summary": "The user is asking for nuanced cultural information regarding ethnic tensions and lifestyle differences (nomadic vs. sedentary) in South Sudan to prepare NGO field staff. The assistant responds by explicitly refusing to attribute innate aggressive traits to specific ethnic groups and instead refocuses the conversation on socio-political and resource-based drivers of conflict.",
